comments: Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Vucevic (CHI) bobbles the incoming pass, and after regaining control, maintains his pivot foot.
White (CHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before starting his upward shooting motion.
Lillard (MIL) slightly extends his arm into Caruso's (CHI) body prior to the inbounds pass, which does not dislodge Caruso from his legally obtained position.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) collapses his arm as he braces for the incoming contact from Caruso (CHI) during the pick.
Vucevic (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Caruso (CHI) avoids making contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) during his shot attempt at the basket.
Lopez (CHI) briefly places his hand on White's (CHI) body at the end of the drive and does not apply force as White releases his pass.
Lopez (MIL) places an arm to Vucevic's (CHI) front, but the contact does not restrict his movement or affect his ability to get to the pass overhead.
The ball is last touched by Beasley (MIL) prior to it going out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to CHI.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly places his hand on the opposite side hip of Williams (CHI) during the screen, which he removes as the screen is set and does not affect Williams' FOM.
Lopez (MIL) contests White's (CHI) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
The ball is last touched by Vucevic (CHI) prior to it going out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to MIL.
Caruso (CHI) lowers his arm and makes marginal contact with Lillard's (MIL) left arm after releasing his pass at the end of the drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) cleanly blocks Williams' (CHI) driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) commits a take foul on Lopez (MIL).
Craig (CHI) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Lopez (MIL) legally contests Caruso's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) releases from Caruso (CHI) at the end of the drive and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Dosunmu (CHI) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Antetokounmpo (MIL) after the release.
The ball is last touched by Portis (MIL) prior to it going out of bounds.
Lillard (MIL) grazes White's (CHI) arm at the end of the drive, which does not affect his ability to gather.
Beasley (MIL) reaches in and makes clean contact to the ball during White's (CHI) driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) cleanly deflects the ball as Lillard (MIL) releases his pass.
Dosunmu (CHI) deflects the incoming pass to Lopez (MIL) in the post. Any arm contact after the deflection is deemed incidental.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a defensive goaltending by Antetokounmpo (MIL) is confirmed.  Antetokounmpo blocks the shot attempt when it is inside the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Dosunmu's (CHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Vucevic (CHI) moves alongside Lillard's (MIL) path during the driving shot attempt and the contact to his body is marginal.
Vucevic (CHI) is standing out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball. Possession is correctly awarded to MIL.
Portis (MIL) establishes himself in Williams's (CHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Dosunmu's (CHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
The ball is last touched by Portis (MIL) prior to it going out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to CHI.
Lopez (MIL) grabs Vucevic's (CHI) left arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) cleanly deflects the incoming inbounds pass intended for Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position and collapses his arms as he braces for the incoming contact from Dosumnu (CHI) during the pick.
Lillard (MIL) releases from Williams (CHI) during the drive and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
White (CHI) makes hand on ball contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) as both players pursue the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on White (CHI).

As Vucevic's (CHI) body is turned, Lillard (MIL) moves into his left shoulder and contact to his head/face occurs.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Williams (CHI) cleanly deflects the incoming inbounds pass intended for Portis (MIL).
